full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/7/2023 OMB #1115-0129 U.S. Department of Justice Application for Replacement of Form I-688A, Employment Authorization, Immigration and Naturalization Service or Form I-688, Temporary Residence Card (Under P.L. 99-603) Please begin with item #1, after carefully reading the instructions.
